metadata.name: Crypto Whales Yacht Club #1
metadata.description: This is a collection of 10,000 NFTs called THE KEY. Crypto Whales Yacht Club membership pass — unique digital collectibles based on the Ethereum blockchain. Whales are graceful and mysterious creatures. They are sociable and nurturing, known for their close friendships and their enthusiasm to innovate, grieve, sing, play, and cooperate with each other.It’s fitting, then, that the Crypto Whales Yacht Club Key provides access to members-only features, including unlockable areas and perks that are strongly focused on communication and collaborative efforts. When you buy the Key, you’re not simply purchasing an avatar or a distinctive piece of art. You are gaining membership access to a club whose benefits and offerings will expand over time. Your Key can become your digital identity, swing open digital doors, and help you to build financial freedom. No other payments are required: the Key is all you need.
